This paper involves natural language processing and computational analysis of a large corpus of sports broadcasts, which suggests that it is likely to belong to the sub-category of Computation and Language (cs.CL). Additionally, the paper deals with issues of bias and fairness, which could fall under the sub-categories of Social and Information Retrieval (cs.SI), Systems and Control (cs.SD), Cybersecurity (cs.CY), and Machine Learning (cs.LG).
